  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">WR + K = high score:</span> WRECK (14 pts) combines two premium consonants. When you hold W+R+K, always check for WR plays before other options.</p>
  </div>
