    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">WRITE extensions:</span> WRITE → WRITES, WRITER, WRITTEN. The base word builds naturally into 6-7 letter plays for bingo potential on subsequent turns.</p>
